F2AUD.original: ~z~Your cousins back in Eastern Europe do this for practically nothing, undercutting us.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你东欧的亲戚们就这样，什么都不做，卖得还比我们便宜。

F2AUD.original: ~z~ -No, no, no, he's...~n~-They better not be filming.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~－不不不，他在...~n~－他们最好没在拍片。

F2AUD.original: ~z~We're going to that sex shop on Hove Beach.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我们要去Hove Beach的色情用品店。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Yes, but you've angered the wrong people.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~不错，但是你惹怒了不该惹的人。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Don't think I cannot see through you.
~z~Point the gun at that guy to his left, Niko.
~z~You need to calm down with that stuff.
~z~You know how much money there is selling this stuff online? A whole fucking heap.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你知道在网上卖这东西能赚多少钱吗？他妈整整一大票。

F2AUD.original: ~z~In my experience... most people, once they change, they stay that way.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~经验之谈...大多数人，一旦改变，这辈子就都这样了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~We're going to an alleyway off of Dillon Street in Schottler.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我们要去一条在Schottler区Dillon街的小巷。

F2AUD.original: ~z~You should have thought of that earlier.
~z~Mr. Faustin, I got a little out of control in the shop, people were hurt.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~Faustin先生，我在店里有点失控了，有人受伤了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~You see, they don't make 'em like that no more.
~z~Mikhail is making enemies very rapidly, a friend like you is useful.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~Mikhail一下子就处处树敌，有个像你这样的朋友会很有用。

F2AUD.original: ~z~We're going to ignore what Mikhail said and try not to kill them.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我们就不管Mikhail说的话，设法留着他们的命。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Mr. Faustin, I don't think you should use that gun shop no more.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~Faustin先生，我觉得你不该再光顾那家枪店了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~You got some money for Mr. Faustin?
~z~In fact, the Mayor of this city tries to shut down Ammu-Nation shops in other states.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~事实上，本市市长还想关闭其他州的武装国度。

F2AUD.original: ~z~No, they just havin' a meeting. I swear...
~z~So, you and Mr. Faustin, have you always argued and made up like this?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~那么，你和Faustin先生，你俩一直都是这样吵着吵着就和解的吗？

F2AUD.original: ~z~that I am a man who appreciates a good business venture when one comes along.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我是个不会放过任何摆在眼前的上好商机的人。

F2AUD.original: ~z~ -Blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah...~n~-Too many bodies, too much attention. We'll be dealt with...
F2AUD.translated: ~z~－废话、废话、废话、都是废话...~n~－尸体太多了、太引人注目了，我们会被一窝端的...

F2AUD.original: ~z~It wasn't always like this. Mikhail was a great man. He had a temper, but he was fair.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~以前不是这样的，Mikhail是个好人。他脾气不好，但他很公正。

F2AUD.original: ~z~This is because guns from them have ended up on the streets here.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~因为他们卖出的枪支流到了这边的街头。

F2AUD.original: ~z~~c~Mikhail... I know you didn't mean it. That's alright.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~~c~Mikhail...我知道你不是那个意思，也行。

F2AUD.original: ~z~How is your cousin, Roman, after the incident the other day?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~之前挨了一枪，现在你堂兄Roman还好吗？

F2AUD.original: ~z~Motherfuckers, you're not treating me like that. I'm a player.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~狗逼玩意，你特么不要那样对我，我可是个玩家。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Now, he blows his top at the slightest thing. I never know who he will shoot, who he will stab.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~现在一点小事都能让他暴跳如雷。我永远不知道他下一枪打谁，下一刀捅谁。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Fine, here you go. We ain't gonna have the...
~z~What the hell did you do that for? How are we supposed to make them pay up now?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~见鬼你干嘛杀了他？我们现在该怎么让他们交钱？

F2AUD.original: ~z~You are a man worth having on our side.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~让你站在我们这边是值得的。

F2AUD.original: ~z~But you treat me like a child.
~z~At least he's alive, eh? Mikhail don't always go for the gut shots.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~至少他还活着，嗯？Mikhail不是每次都朝肚子打的。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Alright, you don't look like a cop. Buy what you want.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，你不像是条子，想买就买吧。

F2AUD.original: ~z~But in ways that will make money. Come back to my house.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~但得是能赚钱的方式。回我家一趟。

F2AUD.original: ~z~His wife, she is a mess. And he does not let up on me. We need the old Mikhail back.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~他的妻子，是一团糟。他也没有放过我，我们想要从前的Mikhail回来。

F2AUD.original: ~z~You can't even hit him in the leg. He has learned at least. Let's go.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你一点也不能打他的腿，你看他至少知道了轻重，我们走吧

F2AUD.original: ~z~So I can be like you, Mr. Barbiturate?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~这样我就能跟你一样了是吧，镇定剂先生？

F2AUD.original: ~z~Word is, they've started their own porno site as well.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~据说，他们还自己开了个黄色网站。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Hey, Joseph! You think you can expand your business interests make these pornos and sell them,
F2AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，Joseph！你以为你在这儿拍片卖片赚大钱，

F2AUD.original: ~z~I didn't kill Joseph, we will make more money with him alive.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我没杀掉Joseph，他活着我们还能大捞特捞。

F2AUD.original: ~z~This guy been making porno in his basement and he didn't cut Mikhail in.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~这家伙在他的地下室拍毛片，还不给Mikhail分账。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Andrei, who you met in Mikhail's basement. He was always loyal, he was a good worker,
F2AUD.translated: ~z~Andrei，你在Mikhail的地下室见着的那个，他一直很忠诚，是个得力干将。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Niko's here. We're going to go take care of that guy.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~Niko来了，我们这就去处理那个人。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Faustin, things got difficult in the shop. I left Dimitri there to deal with it.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~Faustin，店里的事情有点棘手。我把Dimitri留那儿应付了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~You need to control yourself, you could become like Mikhail.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你要控制住自己，不然就会变得跟Mikhail一样了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~No, it's Mikhail that has that issue. Can't keep his finger off of the triggers.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~不，有异议的是Mikhail。他的手指就是离不开扳机。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Mikhail fucked up his guts pretty bad.
~z~This is what you are for, Bellic. To hurt people for me.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~派你去就是为了这个，Bellic。去替我伤人。

F2AUD.original: ~z~It's underground. A backroom place. There are a few around the city.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~地下的。秘密贩卖的地方，城里有好几个。

F2AUD.original: ~z~You guys are getting protection money off of websites now? What, you stop them from getting viruses?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你们现在还要收网站的保护费了吗？怎么，交了钱就不会中病毒？

F2AUD.original: ~z~Mikhail seems to go after those close to him, like Ilyena.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~Mikhail似乎在追逐那些和他亲近的人，比如Ilyena。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Least he could have done is sent over some tapes.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~那他至少也得送两卷带子过来啊。

F2AUD.original: ~z~You trying to tell me I owe you my life?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你是想跟我说我欠你一条命吗？

F2AUD.original: ~z~I'm just in this for the bitches, I don't wanna get hurt! Please. Please. Come on.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我只是为了那些婊子，我并不想伤到谁！拜托拜托，走啊。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Wasn't always like this though. Things got to him.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~以前他不是这样的。只是遇上了各种各样的事。

F2AUD.original: ~z~I got some bad news, Mr. Faustin. Dimitri's gone.
~z~Please, go get us some wheels. I haven't the energy.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~拜托，去给我们弄辆车来，我没那力气。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Taking a bite of this pie would be very profitable for our operation.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~能咬一小口这块蛋糕对我们的运营大有裨益。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, he'll be outta action for a couple a weeks.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~操，他得有几个星期没法下床了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~There is no room for two maniacs in our operation.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我们的生意可顶不住两个疯子。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Mikhail is not most people. He was a great man.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~Mikhail不是大多数人，他曾是一个好人。

F2AUD.original: ~z~I take it you won't be joining us?
~z~It's underground. A backroom place. There are a few around the city.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~地下的。秘密贩卖的地方，城里有好几个。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Screw you, we're seeing a friend of mine who's got a good line on weapons.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~去你的吧，我们要去找我朋友，他在军火上很有路子。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Mikhail gets a taste of any money that gets made in Hove Beach.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~Mikhail渴求在Hove Beach产生的任何收入。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Fuck! You're lucky Roman don't try to make you kill someone every two seconds.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~操！Roman没有隔两秒就让你去杀个人真是你的福气。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Hey man, please? Go easy on me. Come on, big guy?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，伙计，拜托？别那么生气。好啦，大块头？

F2AUD.original: ~z~Alright, alright already. Brett was just trying to be friendly.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~好了，可以了，Brett只是想友善一点。

F2AUD.original: ~z~No, I'm not. I was trying to tell you,
~z~Here, in Liberty City, there is no such thing as the Ammu-Nation.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~在自由城这边，就没有武装国度这回事。

F2AUD.original: ~z~I'll take this one. Charge Mr. Faustin.
~z~that a man like you could be more useful to us alive than dead.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你这样的人活着比死了对我们更有用。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Thank you for your help, Niko. Come to see us at the club soon. Mikhail will be cool by then.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~感谢你的帮助，Niko。过后来俱乐部找我们，到时候Mikhail应该就消气了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, you will. Especially since you got rid of Vlad, our fucking debt collector.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~是的，你会的。更何况你还做掉了Vlad，我们手下的讨债人。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Do you think that I am not to be obeyed? Come back to see me.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你以为我是能被忤逆的人吗？再回来找我。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Mr. Faustin, I couldn't do what you wanted me to.
~z~I want to buy you a present.
~z~You don't know what I can do.
~z~Let me guess, in a prison camp in Siberia.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~容我猜猜，在西伯利亚的集中营里？

F2AUD.original: ~z~The shop is just down that alleyway.
~z~Guns don't seem that controlled. I seen plenty and I just got here.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~感觉枪也没管那么严啊，我刚到这里就见着一堆了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Am I helping pick out a porno for you? I think you know best what you like.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我是要帮你挑片子吗？我觉得你最清楚自己的口味。

F2AUD.original: ~z~You fuckin' Ruskies are milking me dry. I ain't a cow.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你们这些狗逼俄国佬要把我榨干了，我又不是奶牛。

F2AUD.original: ~z~The Mayor has a real hard-on for gun control.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~市长对枪支的管制真的很严。

F2AUD.original: ~z~It was very difficult for me to persuade him
~z~I got carried away and fired all my bullets. Sorry.
~z~Where we would be now if I was calm like you?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~要是我跟你一样冷静，我们现在会在哪儿？

F2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, could be. Depends how things go for me while I'm here.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~确实，有可能。取决于我在这儿遇到什么事。

F2AUD.original: ~z~I'm not saying don't run things your way.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我不是说不按你的方式办事。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Mikhail said something about men suffering. That sounds like some sick shit.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~ Mikhail说是什么折磨，听起来好像很恶心。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Will you wrap it up and put a pretty bow on it?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你会帮我包起来再打个漂亮的蝴蝶结吗？

F2AUD.original: ~z~Fuck, why couldn't you make this easy? We're out of here, Niko.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，你们就不能少整点花活？我们走，Niko。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Don't kill me. I got a load of desperate fans on the internet.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~别杀我，我在网上有很多死忠粉。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Once he learns to control his bowels again he will be good.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~等他学会控制肠子就会好起来的。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Shoot him in the fucking leg, Niko.
~z~I might run into someone I want to shoot.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我可能会碰到我想射杀的人。

F2AUD.original: ~z~As long as that someone is not me or Mikhail, then all is good.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~只要那个人不是我或Mikhail，那就是好的。

F2AUD.original: ~z~If it wasn't for that, I'd say this weren't worth transferring to DVD.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~没有这个镜头，这片就没必要烧成碟了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Always so fucked up on painkillers you don't give shit?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~变成止痛药僵尸，你丫就满意了是吧？

F2AUD.original: ~z~Remind Faustin of that, maybe then he will not try to kill me.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~提醒Faustin这一点，也许那样他就不会想杀我了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~When I have to push people, it's "me".
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我必须得威逼别人的时候，就成「我」了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Do you think that I am not to be obeyed? Come back to see me.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你以为我是能被忤逆的人吗？再回来找我。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, well now it looks like you got me to settle your business.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~操，不过看来现在你还有我能帮你处理事务。

F2AUD.original: ~z~A freak like you should get neutered.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你这样的怪胎就该直接阉了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~And now you'll know where to get them for yourself, what's the problem?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~那现在你就能知道去哪儿能弄到了，有问题吗？

F2AUD.original: ~z~Come on, Niko. Put a cap in his fucking leg.
~z~That's the way it works. I am angry, you are calm.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~套路就是这样的。我负责暴怒，你负责冷静。

F2AUD.original: ~z~I hope it don't get to me.
~z~With a gun you will stay protected, that is the important thing.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~有了枪，你就有了防护，这是很重要的。

F2AUD.original: ~z~When I give out the money, it's "us".
~z~Funny. That ain't it. These guys are making the shit loads of cash,
F2AUD.translated: ~z~有趣。不是这样的，这些家伙赚了大把钞票，

F2AUD.original: ~z~I'm special, I'm gonna be a star. Don't hurt me. A big, big star!
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我很特别，我会成为明星的，别伤害我，我是一颗闪亮的明星！

F2AUD.original: ~z~I think you are safe. For the moment at least.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我想你是安全的，至少暂时如此。

F2AUD.original: ~z~ -Woah, woah... ~n~-and we won't know about it, huh?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~－喔，喔...~n~－还能不被我们知道，是吧？

F2AUD.original: ~z~I said get out of my sight!

F2AUD.translated: ~z~你才要当心点...你越来越疯了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~and we ain't seein' any of it.
~z~Yes, you're right. It looks like I need to protect myself and my cousin in this place.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~是的，你说的对，我似乎是得在这里保护我和我堂兄。
~z~你老家的人交配起来很有趣。

F2AUD.original: ~z~I got something special in these pants, I need to show it to the world.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我裤子里有个特别的东西，我还要向全世界展示它呢。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Listen, big guy. You got a great look going on, real strong. We could put you in one of our films.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~听着，大块头，你看起来很棒，力大无比，你可以来参演我们的片子。

F2AUD.original: ~z~ -Then we was gonna cut you in.~n~-Your books are closed until you pay us our cut.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~－然后再给你们分账。~n~－你先跟我们分完账，然后再核算账簿。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Ammu-Nation, right? Shopping carts full of AK47s...
F2AUD.translated: ~z~武装国度，对吧？购物车里全是AK47...

F2AUD.original: ~z~You got to remember, you killed Vlad. That angered Mikhail no matter what he said.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你要记住，你杀了Vlad，把Mikhail惹怒了，之后他说的都不算数。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Get some transport and take us to Dillon Street in Schottler.
~z~now he is dead. I guess that that is why we need your help.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~现在他死了，我想因此我们才需要你的帮助。

F2AUD.original: ~z~I told you to shoot him in the leg. It matters little. Let's get out of here.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我都跟你说了你开枪打他的腿，不过都没关系了，我们赶紧走吧。

F2AUD.original: ~z~I'm fucking big time, bitches. I'm gonna be a star.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我他妈就是大人物，贱人们，我会成为巨星的。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Pick out what you like. Tell them to put it on Mr. Faustin's account.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~挑个你喜欢的，跟店员说记在Faustin先生账上。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Do not fear. You no longer need to protect yourself from myself and Mikhail.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~不要害怕，很快你就不用防着Mikhail和我了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~You are the one who should be taking Dimitri's sedatives, not me.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~你才是该吃Dimitri的镇静剂的人，而不是我。

F2AUD.original: ~z~This is a mess, let's get out of here.
~z~Joseph, I thought you were a better businessman than this. We go, Niko.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~Joseph，我还以为你是个聪明的生意人，走吧，Niko。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Hey, I heard about these. Big American Supermarket where you can buy any gun you want.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，这我听说过。美国大商场，想买什么枪就买什么枪。

F2AUD.original: ~z~We was just waiting 'til the books was closed at the end of the financial year.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我们只是想等到财年年末把账簿核算完。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Or selling hash to tourists in Red Square, or still in the navy? Which is it today?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~还是在红场卖大麻给游客？还是还在海军待着？哪个会是现在的状况？

F2AUD.original: ~z~I guess Roman's real lucky then. I wonder what big favor Faustin's gonna do for him next?
F2AUD.translated: ~z~那我猜Roman真的很走运了。不过你说Faustin接下来会对他做什么？

F2AUD.original: ~z~if we don't start playing by the rules.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~不能再这样不按规矩胡闹了。

F2AUD.original: ~z~I can't die today. I'm special. I'm really special. I can show you...
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我现在不能死，我很特别、我真的很特别，我可以给你们看看...

F2AUD.original: ~z~Please don't hurt me, I'm an actor.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~求你别伤害我，我只是个演员。

F2AUD.original: ~z~Is that a fact? Maybe we can't pop you, Joseph. But we can fuck up one of your boys.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~这是事实吗？也许我们不能立刻崩了你，Joseph，但我们可以干死你的一个手下。

F2AUD.original: ~z~I hurt the guy who works there.
~z~I got no problem with sparing some lives.
F2AUD.translated: ~z~我对放人一马没有任何异议。
~z~我们都一起混了这么多年了...
